==Ancient Greek==
===Pronunciation===
*γάρ: /gɑɹ/
===Conjunction===
#[[for]]
#[[since]]
====Usage Notes====
Γάρ is a post-positive word, i.e. it is never the first word in a sentence.  It is usually the second, but sometimes also the third or fourth.
